cs.NE, cs.DL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI

The paper discusses the design and development of an integrated environment for computational neuroscience experiments and analysis, which involves data management, imaging technologies, and algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning (cs.DL), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the analysis of large image datasets, which further supports the inclusion of these sub-categories.
